    <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Ensign:Serif&quot;, McKay, &quot;McKay ldsLat&quot;, Palatino, &quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;, Palatino-Roman, serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"><br>
      ＝＝＝</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;,Zoram,&quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;,Arial,sans-serif;"> <br>
    </span><b>贖罪について教えることの大切さ<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Ensign:Serif&quot;, McKay, &quot;McKay ldsLat&quot;, Palatino, &quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;, Palatino-Roman, serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;"></span></b><br>
